refentry.refsect1:
  &reftitle.examples;



    eval 例子 - 简单的文本合并


<?php
$string = 'cup';
$name = 'coffee';
$str = 'This is a $string with my $name in it.';
echo $str. "\n";
eval("\$str = \"$str\";");
echo $str. "\n";
?>


    &example.outputs;


This is a $string with my $name in it.
This is a cup with my coffee in it.

&reftitle.notes;

&note.language-construct;

&tip.ob-capture;



  如果在执行的代码中产生了一个致命的错误（fatal error），整个脚本会退出。
